put your house on it--
boom, you get the house back.

00:30.164 --> 00:32.598
- What the hell's
a vision board?
- Oh, it's The Secret!

00:32.600 --> 00:35.234
Yeah, The Secret
is a self-help book that Dee
read and explained to us.

00:35.236 --> 00:37.870
