how I got the house.

01:12.373 --> 01:15.207
See, I envisioned
the courts recognizing
how ridiculous it was...

01:15.209 --> 01:17.876
that my son of a bitch
asshole mother
didn't leave me anything.

01:17.878 --> 01:20.546
And then I did
some good deeds,
and boom-- I'm rich.

01:20.548 --> 01:22.714
- Mansion rich.
- Whoa, wait a second.

01:22.716 --> 01:25.751
